_sText: I created this for the lazy people that don't feel like making the round corners each time they create a new map. This way, they can just place a simple prefab. They are all 128 untis in height, which is the standard size for a wall. They are in dev textures, so you can texture them whatever you want after. The corners were created using the following tutorials: Creating Rounded Corners Round and Smooth corners with Displacements Enjoy!
